| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7019 — Recovery Inhibition (metaencryptor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 35bc97bb-4044-5e02-a729-8cbba96376ac"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
